Title: There Is No Polynomial Deterministic Space Simulation of Probabilistic Space with a Two-Way Random-Tape Generator  
Author: Marek Karpinski Rutger Verbeek 
Note: Printed in Information and Control 67 (1985), pp. 158-162. Supported by the  
